\s ISHENGERO RY’IMANA
\pc \bdit Shengero ry’Imana, \bdit*\bdit Shengero \bdit*\bdit ry’Umukiza n’ushime unezerwe, umunzero wawe wuzure kuko I Siyoni, I Siyoni mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit juru ku Mana ibudapfa, niho umutima wawe uziritse.\bdit*
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Umwami yavuze ati: nagukunze urukundo rutagira akagero, none se weho umpaye iki isi n’ijuru vyose, ibiyaga imisozi n’inzuzi zitemba bitarabaho nari nkuzi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Shengero ry’Imana, Shengero ry’Umukiza n’ushime unezerwe, umunzero wawe wuzure kuko I Siyoni, I Siyoni mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit juru ku Mana ibudapfa, niho umutima wawe uziritse.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Mbega se womenya, imigabo myiza jewe ngufitiye? Icompa gusa ukanyumvira, wumvire intumwa, wumvire abavugishwa wicishe bugufi, ni ryo shikanwa rimpimbara.\bd*
\pc \bdit Shengero ry’Imana, Shengero ry’Umukiza n’ushime unezerwe, umunzero wawe wuzure kuko I Siyoni, I Siyoni mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit juru ku Mana ibudapfa, niho umutima wawe uziritse.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nta gihe na kimwe wigeze usonza, canke ng’ugw’isari wamye unywa kuri rwa rutare ico ndagusavye n’uce bugufi maze uce aho ngucisha ubone kuragwa ibihoraho\bd*\bd .\bd*
